### **SysBackground.enableFuncaptchaSolver(autoOpen)**

**Description:**
The `SysBackground.enableFuncaptchaSolver(autoOpen)` function enables the automatic solving of FunCaptcha challenges using the `SysContent.enableSafeFuncaptchaSolver` method. The `autoOpen` parameter specifies whether the FunCaptcha anchor should automatically open or not.

**Parameters:**
- **autoOpen** (Boolean): If set to `true`, the FunCaptcha anchor will automatically open. If set to `false`, the anchor will not be opened automatically.

**Example:**

```javascript
SysBackground.enableFuncaptchaSolver(true);  // Automatically open the FunCaptcha anchor and start solving.
```